title: High Fedlity
summary: After discovering a decommissioned machine capable of creating perfect human clones, lonely janitor Tom Wynn secretly replicates himself to maintain his job while he rebuilds his life. As the two versions conspire to clone his ex-girlfriend and escape together, their plan spirals into theft, deception, and quiet betrayal. But when Tom finally leaves with the life he wanted, the version left behind must confront a haunting truth
